e soaring around beautiful islands.\n\nKey Features:\n\n- Pilot 4 distinct aircraft each with their own handling characteristics!\n\n- Soar around 4 unique, beautifully-stylized islands!\n\n- Earn money to buy new airports and new vehicles! Ultrawings is a VR game with REAL progression!\n\n- Tons of gameplay variety! Pop balloons, participate in thrilling air races, fly through score rings, and even perform emergency landings! Ultrawings is the ultimate hobbyist flight game!\n\n- Full VO support guides you through the game!", "short_description": "Use your virtual hands to pilot the Ultralight, rocket-powered Glider, Sport Plane, and Gee Racer to complete a variety of missions across an island-themed world!"}]}, "developer_name": "Bit Planet Games, LLC", "developer_privacy_policy_url": null, "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Bit Planet Games, LLC", "support_website_url": "https://bitplanetgames.com/contact", "website_url": "https://bitplanetgames.com/", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_SOME", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["ADVENTURE", "FLYING", "SIMULATION"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "NO_MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en", "en_US", "ja", "zh_CN", "fr", "fr_CA", "de", "es_MX", "es"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "323124843075418"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 24, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "594175062771417"}, {"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "1105138290378969"}, {"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "1440132803473331"}, {"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "1113987549420354"}, {"status": "P